column32: At Diaverum we are committed to providing you with the best possible care. We kindly ask you to complete two online surveys to find out how you experience the quality of your care. Completing both surveys takes about 15 minutes and will help us to improve the service we provide to you. Your scores and feedback are absolutely confidential. The study is being carried out by Integrated Care Evaluation (ICE) an independent research institute which Diaverum uses to process the data and report to Diaverums management. If you have any questions or would like any further information please contact the research team at info@integratedcareevaluation.orgThank you.
